headline: 1 Volatile Stock with Impressive Fundamentals and 2 to Turn Down
summary: Volatility cuts both ways - while it creates opportunities, it also increases risk, making sharp declines just as likely as big gains. This unpredictability can shake out even the most experienced investors.

headline: NetApp Sets New Standard for Cybersecurity at the Storage Layer
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., April 29, 2025--NetApp® (NASDAQ: NTAP), the intelligent data infrastructure company, today announced new data security capabilities that help customers strengthen their cyber resiliency. Security teams can now leverage NetApp, the most secure storage on the planet, to take a proactive approach to data security at the storage layer and strengthen their overall security posture.
